      <h3 class="heading-serif text-xl tracking-tight mb-3">The Power of .contact</h3>
      <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">The .contact TLD naturally implies connection, inquiry, and professionalism. Perfect for a global booking platform, directory, lead generation engine, or trusted service network.</p>
    </div>

